Actress- turned- entrepreneur Carolyna Hutchings has tackled Tiannah Styling boss, Toyin Lawani for her curiosity over her crashed marriage. In the fourth episode of the reality TV show, The Real Housewives of Lagos, Lawani asked Carolyna to explain the tral reason for her crashed marriage to Musa Danjuma during a truth or dare game. An angry Carolyna took on Lawani, saying, “Toyin should first tell us all bout her baby daddies before asking me about the true story of my divorce. “I can’t imagine how she would bring up such topic in a game of truth or dare.”   Actress Chinedu Bernard slumps in church, dies     Investments in human being best – Obi Cubana     UPDATED: APC yet to zone presidential ticket – Adamu   The cast of the reality TV show gathered at the Transcorp Hilton hotel in Abuja on the invitation of their host and one of the cast, Chioma Ikokwu. The cast, except for Iyabo Ojo, who was on a trip outside Nigeria, flew to Abuja on a private jet for their three-day getaway trip. During one of the nights in Abuja, the ladies decided to switch up the fun by playing a truth or dare game initiated by Carolyna Hutchings when the drama ensued. In the show’s last episode, Carolyna slammed Laura Ikeji in a bitter exchange of words over some reports by Laura’s elder sister, Linda Ikeji, which she alleged crashed her marriage.